+   **Action:**                                                                                                                        
+   - Line 97: Change headroom frame time from 8.3ms → 6.67ms (150fps headroom above 8.33ms 120fps budget)                             
+   - Line 102: Change upscale threshold from 6.0ms → 4.5ms (aggressive reversion to 120fps)                                           
+   **Target Outcome:** Scale responds aggressively to stay under 8.33ms frame budget                                                  
+   **Verify:** Frame time response confirms aggressive scaling                                                                        
+   ---                                                                                                                                
+   Step 2: Modify EMA for Reduced Jitter (15 min)                                                                                     
+   File: luvatrix_core/platform/ios/scene_target.py                                                                                   
+   Lines: 86-91 (present_time_ema calculation)                                                                                        
+   Action: Increase alpha weight from 0.15 → 0.8 (faster convergence, less jitter)                                                    
+   Target Outcome: 20% EMA lag (not 0%) provides reactivity without noise                                                             
+   Verify: Faster response without flickering scale levels                                                                            
+   ---                                                                                                                                
+   Step 3: Increase Render Scale Resolution (15 min)                                                                                  
+   File: luvatrix_core/platform/ios/scene_target.py                                                                                   
+   Line: 58 (levels tuple)                                                                                                            
+   Action: Change to monotonic sequence: (1.0, 0.875, 0.75, 0.625, 0.5, 0.375, 0.25)                                                  
+   Target Outcome: 7 discrete scale levels, 0.125 increments, no typos                                                                
+   Verify: Smooth transitions, text readability at each level                                                                         
+   ---                                                                                                                                
+   Step 4: Implement Frame Budget Enforcement with Inflight Frame Logic (45 min)                                                      
+   File: luvatrix_core/platform/ios/scene_target.py                                                                                   
+   Lines: 747-780 (IOSMetalSceneTarget class)                                                                                         
+   Action:                                                                                                                            
+   - Add frame skip when budget exceeded (8.33ms)                                                                                     
+   - Use inflight frame semaphore from Metal backend to allow CPU prep while GPU finishes                                             
+   - Don't drop frames due to GPU slowness; use async pipeline logic                                                                  
+   Target Outcome: Maintain 120fps by skipping only when Python app loop is bottleneck                                                
+   Verify: Frame skips only when CPU-bound, GPU frames complete while CPU preps                                                       
+   ---                                                                                                                                
+   Step 5: Optimize Metal Pipeline State Caching (30 min)                                                                             
+   File: luvatrix_core/platform/ios/metal_backend.py                                                                                  
+   Lines: 786-920 (pipeline compilation), 525-540 (init)                                                                              
+   Action: Add slots to state class, cache pipeline states instance-level                                                             
+   Target Outcome: Reduced memory footprint, eliminated pipeline compilation overhead                                                 
+   Verify: Monitor memory usage, check startup time improvement                                                                       
+   ---                                                                                                                                
+   Step 6: Align Python Polling with CADisplayLink (50 min)                                                                           
+   File: luvatrix_core/platform/ios/scene_target.py                                                                                   
+   Lines: 547-700 (present_scene method), poll_hdi_events                                                                             
+   Action:                                                                                                                            
+   - Ensure Python-side polling frequency matches CADisplayLink firing rate (120Hz)                                                   
+   - Use shared semaphore for perfect alignment                                                                                       
+   - No CVDisplayLink (macOS-only); use existing CADisplayLink from AppDelegate.swift                                                 
+   Target Outcome: Sub-millisecond timing control synchronized to 120Hz via CADisplayLink                                             
+   Verify: Consistent frame timing, no drift, 120Hz display sync                                                                      
+   ---                                                                                                                                
+   Step 7: Add 120fps Compliance Telemetry (25 min)                                                                                   
+   File: luvatrix_core/platform/ios/scene_target.py                                                                                   
+   Lines: Add new class variables and update methods                                                                                  
+   Action: Track consecutive 120fps frames in 60-frame window                                                                         
